- [x] shared: Add IpcCommand_x (Load/Unload/Status) + IpcResponse_x typer
- [x] Opdater mcp-servers.json med autoload + description
- [x] cargo build ✓

### 6b: IPC gateway (TCP localhost)
- [x] gateway: IpcGateway_gtw — TCP listener (listen) + client (send_command)
- [x] Protocol: JSON lines (request → response, then close)
- [x] cargo build ✓

### 6c: --mode tools (refaktor ProxyAdapter_adp)
- [x] main.rs: Add `--mode` arg (server | tools, default tools)
- [x] adapter: Gem alle ServerConfig_x i catalogue HashMap (fra config)
- [x] adapter: Spawn kun autoload=true servere ved opstart
- [x] adapter: Tilføj IPC listener til event loop (tokio::select!)
- [x] adapter: IPC load → spawn server fra catalogue, send tools/list_changed
- [x] adapter: IPC unload → shutdown server, send tools/list_changed
- [x] adapter: IPC status → returnér liste af servere med running/stopped
- [x] core: tools/list returnerer KUN downstream tools (ingen mcp/* management)
- [x] cargo build ✓

### 6d: --mode server (ProxyAdapter_adp genbrugt)
- [x] adapter: Når mode=server: læs config, byg ét McpTool_x per server
- [x] adapter: Tool name = server id, description fra config
